description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:20:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/no-concrete-step-turkey-brics-membership-erdogans-party-says-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>独家：大众品牌首席执行官表示，大众汽车 CUPRA 面临欧盟计划关税的“风险”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-cupra-at-risk-planned-eu-tariffs-says-brand-ceo-2024-09-03/</link><description>该品牌首席执行官告诉路透社，如果欧盟委员会按照计划对汽车征收 21.3% 的进口关税，那么大众汽车 CUPRA 品牌在中国制造、西班牙设计的电动汽车将被“消灭”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 11:32:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-cupra-at-risk-planned-eu-tariffs-says-brand-ceo-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>韩国恢复申办世界杯，回归的洪希望得到救赎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/returning-hong-eyes-redemption-south-korea-resume-world-cup-bid-2024-09-03/</link><description>韩国队主教练洪明甫周四重返国际赛场，旨在消除过去的失望，并在首尔对阵巴勒斯坦的亚洲世界杯预选赛第三阶段比赛中取得胜利。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 10:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/returning-hong-eyes-redemption-south-korea-resume-world-cup-bid-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>安哥拉权衡中国和欧洲的竞争对手融资以转型经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/angola-weighs-rival-china-european-financing-bids-transform-economy-2024-09-03/</link><description>安哥拉财政部长周二表示，如果安哥拉要吸收更多从太阳能电池板到电动汽车等中国制造的产品，中国需要加大对安哥拉的融资力度，因为这位前欧佩克成员国正在考虑争夺来自北京和欧洲的投标。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 10:41:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/angola-weighs-rival-china-european-financing-bids-transform-economy-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：劳动节到九月开始的劳动报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-03/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 10:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>研究人员称，美国选民受到中国网络影响力的攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-voters-targeted-by-chinese-influence-online-researchers-say-2024-09-03/</link><description>情报公司 Graphika 的最新研究显示，中国的社交媒体影响力行动正在冒充美国选民，诋毁美国政客，并在 11 月 5 日美国总统大选之前传播分裂信息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 10:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-voters-targeted-by-chinese-influence-online-researchers-say-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>据日经新闻报道，苹果将从 2025 年起为所有即将推出的 iPhone 改用 OLED 显示屏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-completely-switch-oled-iphone-display-2025-nikkei-says-2024-09-03/</link><description>日本《日经新闻》周二援引未透露姓名的消息人士的话报道称，苹果将在 2025 年及以后销售的所有 iPhone 机型中使用有机发光二极管 (OLED) 显示屏，完全放弃液晶显示屏 (LCD)。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-completely-switch-oled-iphone-display-2025-nikkei-says-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>尽管有国际刑事法院的搜查令，普京在蒙古仍受到热烈欢迎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-gets-lavish-welcome-mongolia-despite-icc-warrant-2024-09-03/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周二在对蒙古进行国事访问时受到红地毯欢迎，蒙古未能根据国际刑事法院的逮捕令逮捕他，乌克兰批评这是对正义的打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:42:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-gets-lavish-welcome-mongolia-despite-icc-warrant-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>高管表示，沙特阿美仍在寻求交易，同时将雷诺-吉利发动机合资公司的股份维持在 10%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/aramco-still-pursuing-deals-while-keeping-renault-geely-engine-jv-stake-10-2024-09-03/</link><description>一位高级管理人员告诉路透社，国家控股的石油公司沙特阿美公司不打算增加其在燃油发动机合资企业 Horse Powertrain 中 10% 的股份，同时将继续寻求更多交易以扩大其下游业务。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:05:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/aramco-still-pursuing-deals-while-keeping-renault-geely-engine-jv-stake-10-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>汤加领导人表示警察提供“免于恐惧的自由”并支持民主</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tonga-leader-says-police-provide-freedom-fear-support-democracy-2024-09-03/</link><description>汤加总理索瓦莱尼周二在向太平洋岛屿警察局长发表讲话时强调了警察在民主国家提供“免于恐惧的自由”方面的作用，并指出全球主要大国对该地区的关注日益增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 07:18:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tonga-leader-says-police-provide-freedom-fear-support-democracy-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>“香港47”：法院结束香港最大国家安全案件的减刑听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-47-court-wraps-up-mitigation-hearing-citys-largest-national-security-2024-09-03/</link><description>周二，最后一批 45 名香港活动人士在一次具有里程碑意义的国家安全审判中提出了最后的减刑请求，罪名是“阴谋颠覆国家政权”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 04:53:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-47-court-wraps-up-mitigation-hearing-citys-largest-national-security-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>利比亚争端解决在望 油价下跌 5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-fall-weak-demand-overshadows-libya-blockade-2024-09-03/</link><description>由于有迹象表明已达成协议解决导致利比亚生产和出口停止的争端，油价周二下跌 5%，跌至近 9 个月以来的最低水平。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 02:16:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-fall-weak-demand-overshadows-libya-blockade-2024-09-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>